    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈、どうしてここにいるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana‚ what are you doing out here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "ダメ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 15.333333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃の時は、関わろうとしなかったくせに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn’t get involved when Kotono was having trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.333333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 18.633333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "いいでしょ。なんでだろう……\nさくらちゃんの力にはなれそうな気がするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never mind that. I wonder why…\nbut I have the feeling I can help Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.533333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.966666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "……感じるの\nさくらちゃんは、自分の歌を歌ってないって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I sense it.\nI sense that Sakura isn’t singing her own song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "原因が何かは、分からないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know the reason why‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらの心臓は、麻奈のもの――）\n（その答えに、麻奈は辿り着いていないのか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Sakura has Mana’s heart.)\n(Mana hasn’t reached that conclusion.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（今はまだ、想像の外なのだろう）\n（だが、いつその答えを思い付いてもおかしくはない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(It’s probably outside of the scope of her imagination.)\n(But there’s a chance she’ll eventually discover the truth.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4166.6666666666715,
          "startTime": 48.1
        }
