      "text": "（突然、カメラらしきものを抱えた人影が飛び出した）\n（だが顔を確認するより早く、人影は走り去ってしまった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Suddenly‚ someone holding a camera jumps out of the bushes.)\n(But before I can get a look at their face‚ they run away.)",
