      "text": "あ、いや……猫だよ、猫",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ uh‚ it was just a cat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 71.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらとの会話を聞かれただろうか。いや、聞かれて）\n（まずいことは話してないはず。気持ちを切り替えよう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Did they overhear my conversation with Sakura? Well‚ even if they did‚)\n(we didn’t talk about anything problematic. Let’s switch gears.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……さくらの気持ちは分かった\n今まで、気付いてあげられなくてごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel now‚ Sakura.\nSorry I didn’t notice it sooner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。そんなの、他の人には分かりっこないですよ\n……とにかく、今はステージに集中します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no‚ it’s okay. It’s not the sort of thing other people would notice.\nAnyway‚ I’ll turn my focus back to our performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_garden-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "明日起きたら、今話したことは全部忘れて\n大会の最後まで全力で前向きに頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I wake up tomorrow‚ I’ll forget everything I told you‚\nand I’ll stay positive and do my absolute best all the way to the end of the competition!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと、琴乃ちゃんと、麻奈さんのためにも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For my team‚ for Kotono‚ and for Mana’s sake.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
