      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_13_04-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（みんな、琴乃、麻奈――他の誰かのために頑張る）\n（そのことを決して嫌だとは思っていないだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(She vows to work hard for her team‚ Kotono‚ and Mana.)\n(I’m sure she doesn’t feel resentment over it either.)",
